snippet: The number of people who chose or renewed coverage in the latest enrollment period means “the Affordable Care Act is working,” the president said.
abstract: Pres Obama says 11.4 million people have selected private health insurance plans or renewed their coverage under Affordable Care Act in period ending in February 2015.
lead_paragraph: The number of people who chose or renewed coverage in the latest enrollment period means “the Affordable Care Act is working,” the president said.
